-- Failed logon attempts
-- VUL: O19C-00-011500
--
-- Must be separate: a policy auditing only failures cannot be combined with
-- success-auditing actions.
--
-- CRITICAL GRAMMAR: WHENEVER NOT SUCCESSFUL belongs on the AUDIT POLICY
-- (enable) statement, NOT on CREATE AUDIT POLICY. The CREATE statement
-- defines the policy actions; the AUDIT statement controls when to fire it.
--
--   CORRECT:
--     CREATE AUDIT POLICY pname ACTIONS LOGON;
--     AUDIT POLICY pname WHENEVER NOT SUCCESSFUL;
--
--   WRONG (causes ORA-00933):
--     CREATE AUDIT POLICY pname ACTIONS LOGON WHENEVER NOT SUCCESSFUL;
-- =============================================================================

